title: SYMHC Classics: The Dark Legacy of Sea Monkeys
itunes:title: SYMHC Classics: The Dark Legacy of Sea Monkeys
description:
Dipping back to a 2015 episode. Despite all the fun cartoons on the packaging featuring tiny humanoid sea creatures having wacky fun and wearing clothes, Sea Monkeys are just brine shrimp. But the story of Sea Monkeys and their inventor is actually pretty surprising -- and quite dark.
